		<requirements>ID_WOTC_PHB24_CLASS_FEATURE_RANGER_FIGHTING_STYLE</requirements>
		<supports>Fighting Style</supports>
		<description>
			<p>You learn two Druid cantrips of your choice (see the Druid class's section for a list of Druid spells). Guidance and Starry Wisp are recommended. The chosen cantrips count as Ranger spells for you, and Wisdom is your spellcasting ability for them. Whenever you gain a Ranger level, you can replace one of these cantrips with another Druid cantrip.</p>
		</description>
		<sheet>
			<description>You learn two Druid cantrips of your choice. Whenever you gain a Ranger level, you can replace one of these cantrips with another Druid cantrip.</description>
